channel.title: Reflection loader
channel.description:
Hi everyone,
I'm making a reflection explorer. At start I have use runescape.jar to load the client, but now I went to use loader.jar. Some class have the same name in runescape.jar and loader.jar, so I went to know a way to load classes from runescape.jar without get error.
I am using "URLClassLoader" to load the class.
Gabuuzz
